@startuml UEORMS_Sequence_01
!pragma teoz true
autonumber
hide footbox

actor Guest
boundary "Web/Mobile Client" as Client
control "Express API Layer\n(app.js route orchestration)" as API
control "Auth + RBAC\n(requireAuth / permission middleware)" as AuthRBAC
control "Email Service + Queue" as Email
control "Billing Service" as Billing
database "PostgreSQL via Prisma" as DB

== 1) Onboarding, Authentication, and Subscription ==
Guest -> Client : Register / Register+Checkout
Client -> API : POST /api/auth/register or /register/checkout
API -> Billing : fetch public plans / create pending registration
Billing -> DB : Plan, PendingRegistration, Subscription init
DB --> Billing : plan + registration context
Billing --> API : plan decision + payment context
API -> AuthRBAC : create tenant/admin user + hash password + issue JWT
AuthRBAC -> DB : Tenant, User, Role/UserRole inserts
DB --> AuthRBAC : user + tenant created
AuthRBAC --> API : token + identity
API -> Email : send welcome/verification
API --> Client : onboarding success + JWT

Guest -> Client : Login
Client -> API : POST /api/auth/login
API -> AuthRBAC : validate credentials + roles + permissions
AuthRBAC -> DB : User + RolePermission lookup
DB --> AuthRBAC : auth context
AuthRBAC --> API : JWT + claims
API --> Client : login success

Guest -> Client : Forgot password
Client -> API : POST /api/auth/forgot-password -> verify-otp -> reset-password
API -> AuthRBAC : OTP reset flow
AuthRBAC -> DB : PasswordReset + User update
API -> Email : send OTP mail
API --> Client : password reset completed


@enduml